vernac_cmds: Definition binds (x : TVar) (v : A) (E : gen_env A) := get x E = Some v.
Definition all_binds (E F : gen_env A) := forall x v, binds x v E -> binds x v F.
Definition eq (E F : gen_env A) := all_binds E F ∧ all_binds F E.
Notation "x '∹' v '⋲' E" := (binds x v E) (at level 65) : gen_env_scope.
Notation "E '⊏' F" := (all_binds E F) (at level 65) : gen_env_scope.
Notation "E '≍' F" := (eq E F) (at level 68) : gen_env_scope.
Implicit Types xs ys : list TVar.
Theorem ok_dom : forall A (E : gen_env A), List.NoDup (dom E) -> ok E.
induction E using env_ind; intro H_NoDup.
Theorem ok_dom_inv : forall A (E : gen_env A), ok E -> List.NoDup (dom E).
induction E using env_ind; intro Hok.
destruct Hok as [ HokE Hok ] ; destruct Hok as [ Hokx Hdoms ].
Theorem ok_NoDup_dom_eq : forall A (E : gen_env A), ok E <-> List.NoDup (dom E).
intro E; split; [ apply ok_dom_inv | apply ok_dom ]; auto.
Theorem binds_empty : forall A x (v : A), x ∹ v ⋲ (@empty A) -> False.
Theorem binds_single : forall A x y (v w : A), x = y -> v = w -> x ∹ v ⋲ (y ∶ w).
intros A x y v w Heq1 Heq2.
Theorem binds_single_inv : forall A x y (v w: A), x ∹ v ⋲ (y ∶ w) -> x = y ∧ v = w.
intros A x y v w Hbind.
destruct (eq_var_dec x y) as [ Heq | Hneq ].
rewrite Heq in *; clear x Heq.
Theorem binds_singles : forall A x y (v w : A) ys (ws : list A), x = y -> v = w -> x ∹ v ⋲ (y :: ys ∷ w :: ws).
intros A x y v w ys ws Heq1 Heq2.
Theorem binds_singles_inv : forall A x y (v w : A) ys (ws : list A), x ∹ v ⋲ (y :: ys ∷ w :: ws) -> (x = y ∧ v = w) ∨ (x ∹ v ⋲ (ys ∷ ws)).
intros A x y v w ys ws Hbind.
Theorem binds_eq_inv : forall A x (v w : A) (E : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ E -> x ∹ w ⋲ E -> v = w.
intros A x v w E Hbind1 Hbind2.
Theorem binds_concat_r : forall A x (v : A) (F G : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ G -> x ∹ v ⋲ (F & G).
intros A x v F G Hbind.
induction G as [ | G y w IHG ] using env_ind.
destruct (eq_keys_dec x y) as [ Heq | Hneq ].
rewrite <- Heq in *; clear y Heq.
destruct Hbind as [ [ _ Heq ] | [ Hneq Hbind ] ].
assert (get x (F & G & y ∶ w) = get x (F & G)) as Heq.
Theorem binds_concat_l : forall A x (v : A) (F G : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ F -> x ∉ G -> x ∹ v ⋲ (F & G).
intros A x v F G Hbind Hnotin.
induction G as [ | G y w IHG ] using env_ind.
assert (get x (F & G & y ∶ w) = get x (F & G)) as Heq.
Theorem binds_concat_inv : forall A x (v : A) (F G : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ (F & G) -> x ∹ v ⋲ G ∨ (x ∉ G ∧ x ∹ v ⋲ F).
induction G as [ | G y w IHG ] using env_ind; intro Hbind.
destruct Hbind as [ [ Heq_xy Heq_wv ] | [ Hneq_xy Hget ] ].
destruct Hget as [ Hget | [ Hnotin Hget ] ].
assert (get x (G & y ∶ w) = get x G) as Heq.
Theorem binds_belongs : forall A x (v : A) (F : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ F -> x ∈ F.
induction F using env_ind; intro Hbind.
apply binds_empty in Hbind; inversion Hbind.
destruct Hbind as [ Hbind | [ Hnotin Hbind ] ].
Theorem belongs_binds : forall A x (F : gen_env A), x ∈ F -> exists v, x ∹ v ⋲ F.
induction F as [ | F y w IHF ] using env_ind; intro Hbelong.
destruct (eq_keys_dec x y) as [ Heq | Hneq ].
Theorem binds_map : forall A B x (v : A) (E : gen_env A) (f : A -> B), x ∹ v ⋲ E -> x ∹ (f v) ⋲ (map f E).
intros A B x v E f Hbind.
induction E as [ | E y w IHE ] using env_ind.
apply binds_empty in Hbind; inversion Hbind.

intros A B x w E f Hbind.
induction E as [ | E y u IHE ] using env_ind.

intros A x y v w F Hbind Hneq.

rewrite <- Heq1, <- Heq2 in *; clear z u Heq1 Heq2.
destruct (eq_var_dec y z) as [ Heqz | Hneqz ].
rewrite <- Heqz in *; clear z Heqz.

rewrite <- Heq_xy, <- Heq_vw in *; clear y w Heq_xy Heq_vw.
induction F as [ | F z u ] using env_ind.
destruct (eq_var_dec x z) as [ Heq | Hneq ].
rewrite <- Heq in *; clear z Heq.
apply binds_concat_l; [ | apply notin_single; auto ]; auto.

rewrite update_one_concat_r in Hbind; [ | apply belongs_single; auto ].
rewrite update_one_concat_r in Hbind; [ | apply belongs_single; auto ].
rewrite update_one_concat_l in Hbind; [ | apply notin_single; auto ].
destruct (eq_var_dec x z) as [ Heq | Hneq ]; subst.
rewrite update_one_concat_l in Hbind; [ | apply notin_single; auto ].
rewrite update_one_concat_l in Hbind; [ | apply notin_single; auto ].
destruct Hbind as [ Hneq2 | Heq ]; [ | destruct Heq as [ _ Heq ]; destruct Heq; contradiction ].
apply binds_concat_l; [ | apply notin_single; auto ]; auto.
Theorem binds_update_notin : forall A x (v : A) (F G : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ F -> x ∉ G -> x ∹ v ⋲ (F ::= G).

Theorem binds_update_inv : forall A x (v : A) (F G : gen_env A), x ∹ v ⋲ (F ::= G) -> (x ∉ G ∧ x ∹ v ⋲ F) ∨ (x ∈ F ∧ x ∹ v ⋲ G).

intros A x y v E Hneq Hbind.
induction E as [ | E z w IHE ] using env_ind.
destruct Hbind as [ Hbind | [ Hnotin Hbind ] ].
destruct Hbind as [ Hbind | [ Hnotin Hbind ] ].
Theorem binds_all_remove : forall A x ys (v : A) (E : gen_env A), ¬ List.In x ys -> x ∹ v ⋲ E -> x ∹ v ⋲ (E ∖ ys).

Theorem binds_dec_exists : forall A x (E : gen_env A), { v | x ∹ v ⋲ E } + { forall v, ¬ x ∹ v ⋲ E }.

Theorem binds_dec : forall A x (v : A) (E : gen_env A), (forall w w' : A, { w = w' } + { ¬ w = w' }) -> { x ∹ v ⋲ E } + { ¬ x ∹ v ⋲ E }.
intros A x v E Hdec.
elim binds_dec_exists with A x E; intro Hdec2.
elim (Hdec v w); intro Hneq; subst.
assert (v = w) by (apply binds_eq_inv with x E; auto).

Theorem eq_refl : forall A (E F : gen_env A), E = F -> E ≍ F.

unfold eq; intros A E F Heq; destruct Heq; split; auto.
Theorem eq_trans : forall A (E F G : gen_env A), E ≍ F -> F ≍ G -> E ≍ G.
